
---------------------------
INTRODUCTION
---------------------------

---------------------------
INSTALLATION 
---------------------------

To install Report::Trades trades reporting package run
    
    ./install.sh

After installation, run

    report_trades.pl --help

to see the list of available command-line options. You may work with the PostgreSQL 
database either through the command-line or webserver (Mojolicious) interface.

---------------------------
RUNNING WEBSERVER
---------------------------

To start the webserver, use the --webserver command-line switch.

---------------------------
ACCESSING THE DATABASE
---------------------------

The trades database is stored as the PostgreSQL database and is accessed within
Report::Trades via DBD::Pg interface.
